{"tid":1079736,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[隻狼? 一隻狼定兩隻狼呀] [PC/PS4/XBOX] 隻狼討論區 [7]","createTime":"2019-03-27T06:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T04:05:09.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad02259d3c9d9b3d5b78aba2596189b8fcfcb8b","tid":1079736,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpP3BST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpP3BST.jpg&h=0ff6a3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣執錢？<br />\nA:撳實正方就吸錢<br />\n<br />\nQ:點先識破到人？<br />\nA:去搵不死人練一練先<br />\n<br />\nQ:點樣返三年前？<br />\nA:有個阿婆比守護鈴你返去問佛雕師就明<br />\n<br />\nQ:點先盡量避免有龍咳？<br />\nA:即場復活唔會有 個死字完全變紅先會計數<br />\n<br />\nQ:龍咳有無得醫？<br />\nA:有 當有人開始咳 就返去寺院問條女佢會教你點做<br />\n有其他會再加<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=34434&amp;snA=155&amp;tnum=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D34434%26snA%3D155%26tnum%3D20&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5RQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=f7962128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=34434&amp;snA=155&amp;tnum=20</a><br />\n【攻略】各種隱藏內容、NPC位置、收集品串<br />\n由讚美太陽提供"},{"pid":"b7d5606ed6b4b32244400b32c07e3aeb51b7a7cb","tid":1079736,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"年度「受虐」大作《只狼 影逝二度》發佈已經有好幾天了，而大家對於這款遊戲的評價是清一色的「難到想刪遊戲」！畢竟光是一個「守門大將」，像小弟這樣的手殘黨就得打個十幾次...而最近，聽說已經有大神成功無傷擊殺最終BOSS！<br />\n近日，一名叫做「Qtt Six」的玩家在油管上傳了自己最新的《只狼》無傷視頻，其在無傷、無道具、無忍具的情況下擊殺了最終BOSS。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n這是什麼概念？要知道，被葦名弦一郎摸一下都得掉巨多血，要是再被雷劈幾下立馬當場暴斃...更別說後面還有個更變態的葦名一心了。<br />\n而這位玩家，不僅成功地格擋和閃避了葦名一心的所有招式，更是敢拼敢打，後空翻接跳劈，回首掏補突刺，各種微操精細地如同沒有感情的「上分機器」，讓小弟不禁懷疑我和他玩得真的是一個遊戲嗎？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n更厲害的是，這個挑戰過程中沒有使用任何道具和忍具！<br />\n但即便是大神玩家，Qtt Six為了達成這次三分鐘的「三無」擊殺BOSS，也反覆嘗試了有135次，最終耗時4小時才達成，這份耐心和操作水平都讓小弟極（嫉）度（妒）佩服！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n小弟噶綠共：這麼說來只狼的主線流程其實很少啊，主要是靠難度虐我們，如果玩家技術夠好，說不定能趕在2小時前通關退款&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"ca2346b5f61bb67f62e40d407768168913a37cff","tid":1079736,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"有冇ps4 SL方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想2週內開到4結局"},{"pid":"e00b725e01072f00c37095bb78588452576e326d","tid":1079736,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔好劇透！！<br />\n討論劇透內容請四重加密<br />\n啲乜乜點打，物物好難打都透晒劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c2d69eb5a69c41c45bceb8e9337fc22c4979ca","tid":1079736,"uid":80344,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ca2346b5f61bb67f62e40d407768168913a37cff","tid":1079736,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:51:40.000Z","msg":"有冇ps4 SL方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想2週內開到4結局"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:54:13.000Z","msg":"係有心一日開兩個都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使鬼2week"},{"pid":"05a4cf037c59f6d58b6871cfb7df23fa8720ce99","tid":1079736,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"請大家無視第二個post"},{"pid":"fac8b710b8e204641f0632372be5a5db3e1ce939","tid":1079736,"uid":106188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T17:32:12.000Z","msg":"我個fd 一週目 打獅猿 一take pass<br />\n我卡左幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7377ab5aae304548690578a8305fe29473455a","tid":1079736,"uid":397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T19:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644513ad167fb4281bf024cc3d81f099d3f4c65f","tid":1079736,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"